//! # zktempo-verifier
//!
//! Solana Anchor program for the zkTempo.sol verifier. Consumes Groth16
//! proofs of Tempo finality (generated by `zktempo-prover`) and persists
//! the resulting `(slot, state_root)` to a PDA. Downstream programs (e.g.
//! `mppsol_cpi`) read the PDA + verify MPT inclusion proofs to authorize
//! Solana-side settlement of Tempo-originated payments.
//!
//! ## Status
//!
//! Scaffold. Account layouts and instruction interfaces are pinned;
//! instruction bodies are stubs (no Groth16 verification yet — that
//! requires the verification key from M5 milestone). See
//! `../../../spec/verifier.md`.

